column9: The Capital. Art Nouveau architecture (UNESCO). Medieval Old Town.
Jelgava Palace (Rastrelli). Former capital of Courland.
'City where the wind is born'. Port and musical capital.
Second largest city. Daugavpils Fortress. Rothko Center.
Wealthy port city. Blue Flag beach. Cow Parade.
Gateway to Gauja National Park. Hanseatic city.
